to\": 2112}, {\"ngram\": \"the rings\", \"from\": 2152, \"to\": 2161}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The joy I felt wasn't just about winning the gold medal; it was my satisfaction with my gymnastics\\\", Zou said.\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2297, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2288, \"end\": 2291, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zou_people\", \"score\": 0.9973631858452995, \"rank\": 0.0025450868312334105, \"text\": \"Zou\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zou_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zou_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The joy\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2194}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold medal\", \"from\": 2228, \"to\": 2242}, {\"ngram\": \"my satisfaction\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2266}, {\"ngram\": \"my gymnastics\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2285}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Illia Kovtunof Ukraine deservingly won the silver, with a well-executed routine that received 15.500.\", \"from\": 2299, \"to\": 2400, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2314, \"end\": 2321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9998392454425155, \"rank\": 0.00016065191511129733, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the silver\", \"from\": 2338, \"to\": 2348}, {\"ngram\": \"a well-executed routine\", \"from\": 2355, \"to\": 2378}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The silver medal is the first and only medal for Ukraine in gymnastics at this Olympics, and the first ever Olympic medal for Kovtun.\", \"from\": 2401, \"to\": 2534, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2450, \"end\": 2457, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9998392454425155, \"rank\": 0.00016065191511129733, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 2527, \"end\": 2533, \"title\": \