 2617}, {\"ngram\": \"a bronze\", \"from\": 2618, \"to\": 2626}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the women's floor final Rebeca Andrade of Brazil narrowly outscored gold medal favorite Simone Biles 14.166 to 14.133 to take her fourth medal in Paris and first gold medal of the competition.\", \"from\": 2674, \"to\": 2869, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2719, \"end\": 2725, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.901478320036431, \"rank\": 0.10041171092175002, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2823, \"end\": 2828, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999958618, \"rank\": 4.140528919533851e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the women's floor final Rebeca Andrade\", \"from\": 2677, \"to\": 2715}, {\"ngram\": \"gold medal favorite Simone Biles\", \"from\": 2745, \"to\": 2777}, {\"ngram\": \"her fourth medal\", \"from\": 2803, \"to\": 2819}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 2853, \"to\": 2868}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I knew about my capabilities of winning medals, and I gave it my all.\", \"from\": 2871, \"to\": 2941, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my capabilities\", \"from\": 2885, \"to\": 2900}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 2912, \"to\": 2918}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was fighting to finally have a gold, because I wanted that one so badly.\", \"from\": 2942, \"to\": 3016, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a gold\", \"from\": 2973, \"to\": 2979}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am so glad I managed today\\\", Andrade said.\", \"from\": 3017, \"to\": 3061, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3048, \"end\": 3055, \"title\": \"htt