eted at the 1992 and 1996 Games has a total of 7 medals.\", \"from\": 3883, \"to\": 3954, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Miller\", \"from\": 3883, \"to\": 3889}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1992 and 1996 Games\", \"from\": 3906, \"to\": 3929}, {\"ngram\": \"a total\", \"from\": 3934, \"to\": 3941}, {\"ngram\": \"7 medals\", \"from\": 3945, \"to\": 3953}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tied with Vera Caslavska of Czechoslovakia Biles has the second most Olympic medals in history with 11, only behind the legendary Larisa Latynina of the Soviet Union who has 18.\", \"from\": 3955, \"to\": 4132, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3965, \"end\": 3969, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vera_Duckworth\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7017012689994399e-22, \"text\": \"Vera\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vera_Duckworth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vera_Duckworth\"}, {\"begin\": 3983, \"end\": 3997, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Czechoslovakia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9988796364780431, \"rank\": 0.0007773794259667822, \"text\": \"Czechoslovakia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Czechoslovakia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Czechoslovakia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 4085, \"end\": 4100, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larisa_Latynina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Larisa Latynina\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larisa_Latynina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larisa_Latynina\"}, {\"begin\": 4115, \"end\": 4120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.803821469423936e-14, \"text\": \"Union\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phra